

<div class="mt-36 grid ml-50 md:ml-0 md:grid-cols-5 md:w-screen gap-5">
    <div class="xl:col-span-1"></div> @*Div to help grid span page correctly using grids*@
    <div class="lg:col-span-1">
        <div class="bg-gray-800 my-3 p-3 rounded-lg shadow-2xl">
            <h1 class="font-bold text-4xl text-white p-1">Questionnaire Generator</h1>
            <p class="text-white text-2x">With this generator you will be able to fill out a short questionnaire about songs and then get back a playlist of songs that fit your desired input.
                If you like the playlist that is returned, then you will have the option to save it to your own Spotify account!
            </p>
            <br />
            <a asp-controller="Generator" asp-action="Questionaire"
               class="text-white font-bold p-2 rounded-md text-2x hover:bg-gray-700 px-1 border-b-2 border-gray-600">Try it out</a>
            <br />
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="lg:col-span-1">
        <div class="bg-gray-800 my-3 p-3 rounded-lg shadow-2xl">
            <h1 class="font-bold text-4xl text-white p-1">Mood Generator</h1>
