                If you like the playlist that is returned, then you will have the option to save it to your own Spotify account!
            </p>
            <br />
            <a asp-controller="Generator" asp-action="Mood"
               class="text-white font-bold p-2 rounded-md text-2x hover:bg-gray-700 px-1 border-b-2 border-gray-600">Try it out</a>
            <br />
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="lg:col-span-1">
        <div class="bg-gray-800 my-3 p-3 rounded-lg shadow-2xl">
            <h1 class="font-bold text-4xl text-white p-1">Time Generator</h1>
            <p class="text-white text-2x">With this generator you will be able to get a playlist of songs based on the time of day and day of the week.
                If you like the playlist that is returned, then you will have the option to save it to your own Spotify account!
            </p>
            <br />
            <a asp-controller="Generator" asp-action="Time"
               class="text-white font-bold p-2 rounded-md text-2x hover:bg-gray-700 px-1 border-b-2 border-gray-600">Try it out</a>
            <br />
        </div>
